window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>It's not just boba now. Together with his friends, Arthur is at the frontier of the Demon World, building a brand-new town, one stone at a time.</b></p> <p>After one particularly stubborn owl won an argument with the system, Arthur blazed a trail with the rest of his friends toward the frontiers of the demon world. All around him is a world untouched by demons. Now, he needs to tame the wilderness into the shape of a town. Luckily, he has help.</p> <p>Whether it's Mizu building wells or Milo forging tools, Arthur isn't alone in his struggles. The days are long and the work is tough, but Arthur is happy to build the town of his dreams. Literally.</p> <p><i>The third volume in a cozy, slice-of-life fantasy series, Demon World Boba Shop has been described as \"a long, kind hug from someone who loves you without wanting anything from you whatsoever.\" It's a cozy, feel-good story, perfect after a long day of work or with a warm (or cold) cup of tea.</i></p>"; 
